Table 2 shows the crude and adjusted associations between change in PAEE (kJ kg−1 FFM min−1), \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
